<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1485572-am-i-the-only-one-that-raised-my-eyebrows">Am I the only one that raised my eyebrows at the description of working in the potato fields as a child? Page 72 states: You picked the spuds by hand, getting only 8 to 10 cents for a bushel. My job when I was small was to run up ahead and shake the spuds loose from the vines so the others could come along and pick them up more quickly. I&#39;m a gardener and I have never seen a potato that grows on a vine.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1485572'><a id="like_count_community_question_1485572" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/1485572?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">1 like</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F108435.Prison_Writings">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
