<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/72900896-christi-koenig"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1508778480i/72900896._UX100_CR0,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/72900896-christi-koenig">Christi Koenig</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">All I can think is, maybe, they plowed along the row of potato vines, exposing the roots with potatoes attached, and he was shaking the potatoes from <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">All I can think is, maybe, they plowed along the row of potato vines, exposing the roots with potatoes attached, and he was shaking the potatoes from the root part of the vines. My parents have potatoes in their home garden, and Dad will plow beside the rows, which makes them easier to dig and pick up. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
