    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1461011010" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7737591407473582508">What a powerful narrative from an extraordinary man. Peltier demonstrates the mistreatment and incarceration of Native men and women through his own testimony. It is well written and forces the reader to see things from another perspective while challenging all of humanity to make a change. Free Leonard Peltier!</span>

          </span>
        </div>


