      <div id="aboutAuthor" class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/author/show/62758.Leonard_Peltier">About Leonard Peltier</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class='bookAuthorProfile'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__topContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/62758.Leonard_Peltier"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1208031912p3/62758.jpg);'></div>
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__widgetContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__name'>
<a href="/author/show/62758.Leonard_Peltier">Leonard Peltier
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__followerCount'>
47
followers
</div>

</div>
</div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer6754274180060632232">Native American politicial activist imprissoned since 1977 accused of shooting two FBI officers. <br/><br/>Peltier is considered to be a political prisoner by amnesty international and the European parlement. <br/><br/>His parole has been denied by Bill Clinton and George W. Bush. </span>

</div>
</div>

<div class="clear"></div></div></div><div class="bigBoxBottom"></div></div>

  

